# ============================================================================
# generated/
#
# This directory contains auto-generated shell files transpiled from the
# SSOT TOML source files in ssot/.
#
# DO NOT EDIT files in this directory manually.
#
# Regenerate all files:
#   just generate-all
#
# Regenerate individual files:
#   just generate-aliases
#   just generate-colors
#   just generate-icons
#   just generate-highlights
#
# Files:
#   aliases.zsh      - Shell aliases for ZSH
#   aliases.fish     - Shell aliases for Fish
#   aliases.nu       - Shell aliases for Nushell
#   aliases.bash     - Shell aliases for Bash
#   colors.zsh       - Color palette definitions
#   icons.zsh        - Nerd Font icon definitions
#   highlights.zsh   - Syntax highlighting rules
#
# Source: ssot/aliases.toml, ssot/colors.toml, ssot/icons.toml,
#         ssot/highlights.toml
# ============================================================================
